Create an App
Set Up Navigation Through Your App

Customize app navigation so that users can easily find the dashboards and lenses targeted for them.

To edit and save navigation lists in CRM Analytics apps:

 View DeveloperName, View Setup and Configuration

Open the navigation list by clicking the disclosure triangle next to the app name.
If you're the manager of an app, click Edit List.
Change the presentation order by sliding Selected Assets up or down.
Add available dashboards or lenses by selecting them and clicking the right arrow.
Hide assets from the navigation list by selecting them and clicking the left arrow.
Retain the navigation for your app by clicking Save.

Share the app with colleagues or customers. When they run the app, it starts with the first asset in your navigation list.
title: Customizing App Navigation in Salesforce CRM Analytics
